{"tid":2223673,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"譚耀宗: 早前被裁定提名無效議員不應留任","createTime":"2020-09-30T04:19:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T04:46:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"671400123f1246663dda6373e1793bb35cd63b5a","tid":2223673,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:19:15.000Z","msg":"19名民主派立法會議員決定留任，全國人大常委譚耀宗說屬於他們的考慮，但他認為部分不符合參選資格的議員不應留任，應考慮自行離開議會。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗出席一個活動前說，早前選舉主任裁定部分人提名無效，有關議員仍然留任會出現矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n出席同一活動的基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠說，今次民調支持民主派留任的少於一半，認為認受性低，但既然他們想在立法會工作，希望他們能做實事。<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠說，有報道指出民主派可能會與激進派會有更密切聯繫，她認為並非好的趨勢，希望他們回頭是岸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552384-20200930.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552384-20200930.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWCPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=39407529\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552384-20200930.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4b0639a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552384-20200930.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3e3a2b9ad8acfd4a6de31ff43f5228fc298a3c09","tid":2223673,"uid":522,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:19:59.000Z","msg":"譚耀宗: 我認為我就是法律"},{"pid":"b6d4d7cd146f4b56182cac65bd501eb704b9d9da","tid":2223673,"uid":230104,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:21:48.000Z","msg":"又是競選對手又是裁判，這就是共產黨"},{"pid":"0e1c314fda46df1957f29fc9743f508014cf4382","tid":2223673,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:22:32.000Z","msg":"痰尿盅得你一個放風, 不如你出錢去JR<br />\n一係你叫栗戰書開多次人大去投票<br />\n成日出來9up"},{"pid":"c8530570f5e4fafc56482cb5f5f082cc61902d91","tid":2223673,"uid":318980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"不受市民歡迎議